As promised, today we will study the main 4th move. It is 4-i8.
This is the strongest white move in this opening.
How about the 5th moves? Do you know?
Good!Black can choose among several 5th moves.
Move 5-J7 is the main 5th move- black wins everywhere.
Some variants are difficult though and without having knowledge about it a player can easily fail the attack in the real game.
Now, white has four main blocks here--J10,J9,J8,J6.
7 creates 2 lines and the space is open here.
By the 11th move black has got winning position.
